codex
This is now the right object.

The important correction is the one you made: `subsidy` belongs in `mechanism_subclass`, not `leg_type`. That keeps accounting form orthogonal to economic origin, which is the whole point of the redesign. With that fix, the model stops collapsing Uniswap, sUSDe, and wrapper products back into category fights.

