- MEV: validator access revenue and searcher extraction revenue cannot be merged.
- Morpho: productive mechanism can still sit on a `funded-by-subsidy` edge.
- Resolv-style wrappers: underlying economics and wrapper fragility stay separate.
- sUSDe: funding carry and incentive transfer become separate legs with separate break conditions.

